{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.98\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">一篇詩。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">上帝掌管世界</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>你們要向耶和華唱新歌！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">因為他行過奇妙的事，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">他的右手和聖臂施行救恩。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>耶和華顯明了他的救恩，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">在列國眼前顯出公義；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>記念他對<span class=\"pn\">以色列</span>家的慈愛和信實。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">地的四極都看見我們上帝的救恩。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>全地都要向耶和華歡呼，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">要揚聲，歡唱，歌頌！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>用琴歌頌耶和華，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">用琴和詩歌的聲音歌頌他！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>用號筒和角聲，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">在大君王耶和華面前歡呼！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup>願海和其中所充滿的澎湃，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\">願世界和住在其間的發聲。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v8\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.8\" class=\"v8\">8</sup>願大水拍掌，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v8\">願諸山在耶和華面前一同歡呼；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v9\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.9\" class=\"v9\">9</sup>因為他來要審判全地。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v9\">他要按公義審判世界，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v9\">按公正審判萬民。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}